(54) Bezeichnung: MONTAGEVORRICHTUNG FUR GETRIEBE SOWIE VERFAHREN ZUR EINSTELLUNG DES ZAHN
The invention relates to a device for
mounting gear mechanisms, especially differential gears,
comprising a manufacturing unit (24) for assembling
housing parts of said gear mechanism, measuring the
bearing surfaces (9,10) or the bores for the bearings (7,8)
of the toothed gear axes (3,4) on the housing (2) of the
gear mechanisms, the relative positions of the toothed
gear axes (3,4) or the possible intersection points or the
distance of the toothed wheel axes (3,4) in relation to each
other, and a measuring device (21) measuring the roll of
2 the pair of toothed gears, are connected to a control device
for the transmission of data and control signals.
